/infra/                @jpj-youtube-ai

# CI/CD pipelines and repo automation
/.github/              @jpj-youtube-ai

# Config surface + secret wiring (golden rule 3)
/src/config/           @jpj-youtube-ai

# Database migrations — can break prod data (expand-contract, golden rule 2)
/migrations/           @jpj-youtube-ai

# Container build — defines the deployed artifact
/Dockerfile            @jpj-youtube-ai

# The project ground rules themselves
/CLAUDE.md             @jpj-youtube-ai
